subject_information.comments: I didn't like how on certain objects I couldn't answer my partner's questions.  These were ones where I had to use a response already prepared for me, and it was usually vague and needed clarification that they asked for and  I wanted to give but was prevented from doing.
subject_information.strategy: I just told them to move the object in the direction of the arrow.  If I couldn't tell what the object was I tried to describe the shape and failed.  Then I tried to just guess what it night have been and said that and it worked.
